---
title: _fft_field (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_check_base : check len(vals) == 1
    q_check_base --> q_return_base : len(vals) == 1
    q_check_base --> q_recurse : len(vals) > 1
    q_return_base --> [*] : return vals
    q_recurse --> q_split : L = _fft_field(vals[even], roots[even])
    q_split --> q_split_r : R = _fft_field(vals[odd], roots[even])
    q_split_r --> q_init_output : o = [BLSFieldElement(0) for _ in vals]
    q_init_output --> q_butterfly : i < len(L)
    q_init_output --> q_return : i >= len(L)
    q_butterfly --> q_combine : y_times_root = y * roots_of_unity[i]
    q_combine --> q_mul : o[i] = x + y_times_root
    q_mul --> q_upper : o[i + len(L)] = x - y_times_root
    q_upper --> q_butterfly : i < len(L)
    q_upper --> q_return : i >= len(L)
    q_return --> [*] : return o

    note right of q_init
        INV: len(vals) must be a power of 2
        INV: len(vals) == len(roots_of_unity)
        INV: Recursive calls halve the input size at each level
    end note
